        "{\"listOfEpisodes\":[{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/20849\"}},\"airdate\":\"2014-10-20\",\"airstamp\":\"2014-10-21T00:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":20849,\"name\":\"Cars, Buses and Lawnmowers\",\"number\":1,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby learns about a character design contest featuring the ultimate prize - a chance to meet idol Mac McCallister and debut an animated character on TV. He plans to attend with Fish and Eli, but when they unexpectedly get stranded at school hours before the contest, they devise a plan that accidently places them in the middle of \\\"Clown Town,\\\" an abandoned area of the city where creepy clowns reign. Meanwhile, Dawn realizes Kirby is using an embarrassing drawing of her titled \\\"Dawnzilla\\\" as his submission for the contest, so she and Belinda do everything in their power to stop him.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/20849/kirby-buckets-1x01-cars-buses-and-lawnmowers\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/20850\"}},\"airdate\":\"2014-10-27\",\"airstamp\":\"2014-10-27T23:30:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"19:30\",\"id\":20850,\"name\":\"Flice of the Living Dead\",\"number\":2,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby and his friends are excited that they\\u0027re finally old enough to attend the annual \\\"Forest Hills Ninth Annual Fright Night Film Festival.\\\" However, when their biology teacher accidentally breaks open a container of Forest Hills Super Flice, the principal quarantines Kirby\\u0027s class within the school, ruining their chance to go. Meanwhile, Dawn and Belinda are psyched to be invited to a Halloween party at the house of one of the coolest boys in school, Evan.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/20850/kirby-buckets-1x02-flice-of-the-living-dead\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/30680\"}},\"airdate\":\"2014-11-03\",\"airstamp\":\"2014-11-04T01:30:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:30\",\"id\":30680,\"name\":\"The Legend of Prank Williams Jr.\",\"number\":3,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby tries to replicate the most outrageous prank ever pulled.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/30680/kirby-buckets-1x03-the-legend-of-prank-williams-jr\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/40005\"}},\"airdate\":\"2014-11-10\",\"airstamp\":\"2014-11-11T00:30:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"19:30\",\"id\":40005,\"name\":\"The Year of Fridays\",\"number\":4,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby is grounded and forced to camp out in the backyard with his dad. Meanwhile, Dawn tries to meet her favorite band.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/40005/kirby-buckets-1x04-the-year-of-fridays\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/45825\"}},\"airdate\":\"2014-11-17\",\"airstamp\":\"2014-11-18T01:30:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:30\",\"id\":45825,\"name\":\"Kirby Almighty\",\"number\":5,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWhen Kirby starts using a pen that appears to have magical powers, everything he draws suddenly starts coming to life.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/45825/kirby-buckets-1x05-kirby-almighty\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/45826\"}},\"airdate\":\"2014-11-24\",\"airstamp\":\"2014-11-25T02:30:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"21:30\",\"id\":45826,\"name\":\"Killer Puppies\",\"number\":6,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eTo avoid getting graded on a bad cooking project, Kirby fakes an illness and is sent to the nurse who takes his fabricated over-the-top symptoms seriously. When the school finds out he supposedly has a serious illness, they shower him with sympathy, gifts and host a fundraiser to raise money to help him get better leaving Kirby worried that his secret will be exposed.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/45826/kirby-buckets-1x06-killer-puppies\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/57244\"}},\"airdate\":\"2014-12-01\",\"airstamp\":\"2014-12-02T02:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"21:00\",\"id\":57244,\"name\":\"Art Attack\",\"number\":7,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eAfter being rejected from the school art fair, Kirby meets the leader of an underground group of artists and is immediately accepted into their ranks. Meanwhile, Dawn discovers Eli was once a toddler model.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/57244/kirby-buckets-1x07-art-attack\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/129035\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-02-02\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-02-03T01:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":129035,\"name\":\"Kirby\\u0027s Choice\",\"number\":8,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby wins tickets to a video game convention but can\\u0027t decide on whether he should take Fish or Eli. To help make his decision, he envisions how the day might go with each of them. Dawn also takes part in the convention when she lands a job dressing up as a comic-book character.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/129035/kirby-buckets-1x08-kirbys-choice\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/128828\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-02-09\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-02-10T01:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":128828,\"name\":\"Mac\\u0027s Back\",\"number\":9,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby\\u0027s favorite show \\\"Big Bald Oaf\\\" has been cancelled leaving the series\\u0027 creator Mac McCallister depressed. Kirby and his friends work to get the show back on the air.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/128828/kirby-buckets-1x09-macs-back\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/128829\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-02-23\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-02-24T01:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":128829,\"name\":\"Kick the Bucket\",\"number\":10,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eSomeone is defacing school property with cartoon murals and signing them with Kirby\\u0027s name, getting him in trouble at school. Kirby and Dawn team up to solve the case.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/128829/kirby-buckets-1x10-kick-the-bucket\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/141518\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-03-16\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-03-17T00:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":141518,\"name\":\"It\\u0027s a Brad, Brad, Brad, Brad World\",\"number\":11,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby is ridiculed at school after causing a toilet to explode. To avoid being teased on the way home, Kirby and his friends venture into The Bradlands, a part of town that only Brads live, and stumble upon buttons which he uses in an attempt to win over the school.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/141518/kirby-buckets-1x11-its-a-brad-brad-brad-brad-world\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/141519\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-03-23\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-03-24T00:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":141519,\"name\":\"Gimme Some Room\",\"number\":12,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWhen a spare room becomes available in the Buckets household, Kirby and Dawn have different ideas on the best way to use it. After Kirby makes Pearly Todd look like a fool in front of the whole school, Kirby agrees to set Todd up on a date with Dawn.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/141519/kirby-buckets-1x12-gimme-some-room\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/151668\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-04-27\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-04-28T00:30:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:30\",\"id\":151668,\"name\":\"Day of the Cat\",\"number\":13,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003ePrincipal Mitchell enlists Kirby\\u0027s help to draw a portrait of his celebrity cat, Laughy Cat. Meanwhile, Dawn gets a card on her locker from a secret admirer.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/151668/kirby-buckets-1x13-day-of-the-cat\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/162890\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-06-17\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-06-18T02:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"22:00\",\"id\":162890,\"name\":\"The Rise and Fall of 4th Period\",\"number\":14,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby becomes the leader of his class after his teacher leaves, creating a fun and chaotic classroom. Dawn and Belinda go on a hygiene strike after the Principal bans hair-dryers.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/162890/kirby-buckets-1x14-the-rise-and-fall-of-4th-period\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/162891\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-06-24\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-06-25T00:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":162891,\"name\":\"The Hurt Box\",\"number\":15,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eWhen Kirby\\u0027s underground comic book that mocks Forest Hills\\u0027 teachers is accidently put in the school\\u0027s suggestion box, Kirby, Fish and Eli devise a plan to steal it back before it\\u0027s too late.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/162891/kirby-buckets-1x15-the-hurt-box\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/182158\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-07-01\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-07-02T00:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":182158,\"name\":\"Get a Grip\",\"number\":16,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby, Eli and Fish are hard at work on their project for the science fair -- creating the Ultimate High Five. Kirby suffers an injury while working on the project that constrains his creative outlet and forces him to start acting out like his characters.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/182158/kirby-buckets-1x16-get-a-grip\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/182305\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-07-08\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-07-09T00:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":182305,\"name\":\"All Hands on Dexter\",\"number\":17,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby and Fish enter a contest to see who can keep his or her hands on a video game the longest. Meanwhile, Mr. Buckets wants to cash in his \\\"Chore Day\\\" coupon from five years ago.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/182305/kirby-buckets-1x17-all-hands-on-dexter\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/182306\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015-07-15\",\"airstamp\":\"2015-07-16T00:00:00+00:00\",\"airtime\":\"20:00\",\"id\":182306,\"name\":\"The Av Kid\",\"number\":18,\"runtime\":30,\"season\":1,\"summary\":\"\\u003cp\\u003eKirby needs a video of him losing a rap-battle to his mom taken down from the internet, so he enlists a member of the AV Club to help. Dawn becomes obsessed with bubble wrap.\\u003c/p\\u003e\",\"type\":\"regular\",\"url\":\"https://www.tvmaze.com/episodes/182306/kirby-buckets-1x18-the-av-kid\"},{\"_links\":{\"selfDomain\":{\"href\":\"https://api.tvmaze.com/episodes/182307\"}},\"airdate\":\"2015